DataSource.SelectSQLQuery: SELECT A.NOTE_ID, A.NOTE_NM, A.NOTE_TXT, A.NOTE_TYPE, A.NOTE_STTS_CD, A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR, A.NOTE_PARNT_ID, A.LST_CHG_USR, A.LST_CHG_TMS, A.CREATD_USER_ID, A.CREATD_TM_STMP, B.CD_DESC_TXT,A.LGCY_IND FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR A, ITEM B WHERE A.NOTE_ID = ? and A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = ? AND (A.NOTE_TYPE = B.PRMRY_CD(+) AND B.CTLG_ID(+) = 1945)
SELECT note_id, note_vrsn_nbr FROM nmst_note_mstr WHERE note_stts_cd = 'PUBLISHED' AND note_parnt_id IN (SELECT note_parnt_id FROM nmst_note_mstr WHERE note_id = {0})

SELECT A.NOTE_ID, A.NOTE_NM, A.NOTE_TXT, A.NOTE_TYPE, A.NOTE_STTS_CD, A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR, A.NOTE_PARNT_ID, A.LST_CHG_USR, A.LST_CHG_TMS, A.CREATD_USER_ID, A.CREATD_TM_STMP FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR A WHERE UPPER(A.NOTE_NM) = UPPER({0}) AND A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = (SELECT MAX(NOTE_VRSN_NBR) FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR WHERE UPPER(NOTE_NM)= UPPER({0}) AND NOTE_STTS_CD != 'MARKED_FOR_DELETION')

SELECT a.note_id, a.note_nm, a.note_txt, a.note_type, a.note_stts_cd, a.note_vrsn_nbr, a.note_parnt_id, a.lst_chg_usr, a.lst_chg_tms, a.creatd_user_id, a.creatd_tm_stmp FROM nmst_note_mstr a WHERE UPPER (a.note_nm) = UPPER ({0}) AND a.LGCY_IND ='N' AND a.note_vrsn_nbr = NVL( (SELECT MAX (note_vrsn_nbr) FROM nmst_note_mstr WHERE UPPER (note_nm) = UPPER ({0}) AND note_stts_cd != 'MARKED_FOR_DELETION'), (SELECT MAX (note_vrsn_nbr) FROM nmst_note_mstr WHERE UPPER (note_nm) = UPPER ({0}) ) )
-- SELECT A.NOTE_ID, A.NOTE_NM, A.NOTE_TXT, A.NOTE_TYPE, A.NOTE_STTS_CD, A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR, A.NOTE_PARNT_ID, -- A.LST_CHG_USR, A.LST_CHG_TMS, A.CREATD_USER_ID, A.CREATD_TM_STMP -- FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR A WHERE UPPER(A.NOTE_NM) = UPPER({0}) AND A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = (SELECT MAX(NOTE_VRSN_NBR) -- FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR WHERE UPPER(NOTE_NM)= UPPER({0}) AND NOTE_STTS_CD != 'MARKED_FOR_DELETION')

SELECT A.NOTE_ID, A.NOTE_NM, A.NOTE_TXT, B.CD_DESC_TXT, A.NOTE_STTS_CD, A.NOTE_TYPE, A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR, A.NOTE_PARNT_ID, A.LST_CHG_USR, A.LST_CHG_TMS, A.CREATD_USER_ID, A.CREATD_TM_STMP FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR A, ITEM B WHERE ( UPPER(A.NOTE_NM) = UPPER({0})) and A.NOTE_TYPE = B.PRMRY_CD and B.CTLG_ID = 1945 ORDER BY A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR DESC

SELECT A.NOTE_ID, A.NOTE_NM, A.NOTE_TXT, B.CD_DESC_TXT, A.NOTE_STTS_CD, A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR, A.NOTE_PARNT_ID, A.LST_CHG_USR, A.LST_CHG_TMS, A.CREATD_USER_ID, A.CREATD_TM_STMP FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR A, ITEM B WHERE ( UPPER(A.NOTE_NM) = UPPER({0})) and A.NOTE_TYPE = B.PRMRY_CD and B.CTLG_ID = 1945 and A.NOTE_PARNT_ID NOT IN {1} ORDER BY A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR DESC

select distinct(A.NOTE_ID),A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR from
NMST_NOTE_MSTR A,
(select max(NOTE_VRSN_NBR) versionNumber,NOTE_ID from NMST_NOTE_MSTR where NOTE_ID = {0} and NOTE_STTS_CD ='PUBLISHED' group by NOTE_ID)AA
where AA.versionNumber = A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR and AA.versionNumber != {1} and A.NOTE_ID = {2}

Select NOTE_ID,NOTE_STTS_CD from NMST_NOTE_MSTR where NOTE_ID = (Select NOTE_ID from NOTE_DOMN_ASSN where ENTY_TYPE ='ATTACHCONTRACT' AND ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({0})) AND NOTE_VRSN_NBR =(Select NOTE_VRSN_NBR from NOTE_DOMN_ASSN where ENTY_TYPE ='ATTACHCONTRACT' AND ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({1}))

SELECT a.note_id, ds.dt_sgmnt_efctv_dt FROM nmst_note_mstr a, cntrct_dt_sgmnt ds, (SELECT note_id, note_vrsn_nbr, enty_sys_id FROM note_domn_assn WHERE enty_sys_id IN (SELECT TO_CHAR (a.dt_sgmnt_sys_id) FROM cntrct_dt_sgmnt a,cntrct_dt_sgmnt_assn b WHERE b.cntrct_sys_id = {0} AND a.dt_sgmnt_sys_id=b.dt_sgmnt_sys_id AND a.dt_sgmnt_test_prod_ind = 'N') AND enty_type = 'ATTACHCONTRACT') attched_note WHERE a.note_id = attched_note.note_id AND a.note_vrsn_nbr = attched_note.note_vrsn_nbr AND ds.dt_sgmnt_sys_id = attched_note.enty_sys_id AND a.note_stts_cd = 'MARKED_FOR_DELETION'
CALL COPYNOTESPROC({0},{1},{2},{3},{4},{5})

SELECT A.NOTE_ID, A.NOTE_NM, A.NOTE_TXT, A.NOTE_TYPE, A.NOTE_STTS_CD, A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR, A.NOTE_PARNT_ID, A.LST_CHG_USR, A.LST_CHG_TMS, A.CREATD_USER_ID, A.CREATD_TM_STMP FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR A WHERE UPPER(A.NOTE_NM) = UPPER({0}) AND A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = (SELECT MAX(NOTE_VRSN_NBR) FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR WHERE UPPER(NOTE_NM)=({0}))

SelectSQLQuery.name: searchNotes
SelectSQLQuery.STATIC:
SELECT DISTINCT a.NOTE_ID, a.NOTE_NM, a.NOTE_TXT, a.NOTE_TYPE, a.NOTE_STTS_CD, a.NOTE_VRSN_NBR,
a.NOTE_PARNT_ID, a.LST_CHG_USR, a.LST_CHG_TMS, c.CD_DESC_TXT
FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR a, NOTE_DOMN_ASSN b, ITEM c
WHERE a.note_id= b.note_id and a.NOTE_TYPE = c.PRMRY_CD AND a.NOTE_TYPE = c.PRMRY_CD AND c.CTLG_ID = 1945 AND a.LGCY_IND = 'N'
SelectSQLQuery.DYNAMIC: and a.NOTE_ID in (select distinct m.NOTE_ID from NOTE_DOMN_ASSN m where m.ENTY_SYS_ID {2} and m.ENTY_TYPE ='SYSTEM DOMAIN')
SelectSQLQuery.STATIC: AND a.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = (select max(d.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) from NMST_NOTE_MSTR d where UPPER(d.NOTE_NM) = UPPER(a.NOTE_NM)) ORDER BY a.NOTE_NM ASC

DataSource.SelectSQLQuery: SELECT n.NOTE_ID ,n.NOTE_NM,MAX(n.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN d, NMST_NOTE_MSTR n WHERE d.NOTE_ID = n.NOTE_ID AND d.NOTE_VRSN_NBR=n.NOTE_VRSN_NBR AND d.ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({0}) AND d.ENTY_TYPE = {1} AND n.NOTE_STTS_CD='PUBLISHED' AND n.NOTE_NM like upper({4}) AND n.NOTE_ID NOT IN (SELECT a.NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN a WHERE a.ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({2}) AND a.ENTY_TYPE = {3}) group by n.NOTE_ID ,n.NOTE_NM UNION SELECT DISTINCT N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM, MAX (N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR N, (SELECT DISTINCT D.NOTE_ID, D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN D, (SELECT N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM, MAX (N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) NOTE_VRSN_NBR FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN D, NMST_NOTE_MSTR N WHERE D.NOTE_ID = N.NOTE_ID AND D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR=N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR AND N.NOTE_STTS_CD='PUBLISHED' AND N.LGCY_IND ='N' GROUP BY N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM ) N WHERE D.NOTE_ID = N.NOTE_ID AND D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR=N.NOTE_VRSN_NBR AND D.ENTY_TYPE ='SYSTEM DOMAIN' MINUS SELECT DISTINCT a.note_id, MAX (a.note_vrsn_nbr) FROM note_domn_assn a, nmst_note_mstr n WHERE enty_type IN ('AVAILBENEFIT', 'AVAILCOMP', 'AVAILPRODUCT', 'AVAILQUALIFIER', 'AVAILTERM', 'AVAILQUESTION' ) AND a.note_id = n.note_id AND n.note_stts_cd = 'PUBLISHED' AND a.note_vrsn_nbr = n.note_vrsn_nbr GROUP BY a.note_id) D WHERE D.NOTE_ID = N.NOTE_ID AND N.NOTE_STTS_CD='PUBLISHED' AND n.NOTE_NM like upper({4}) AND N.NOTE_ID NOT IN (SELECT a.NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN a WHERE a.ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({2}) AND a.ENTY_TYPE = {3}) GROUP BY N.NOTE_ID, N.NOTE_NM

SELECT DISTINCT n.NOTE_ID ,n.NOTE_NM , D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR ,n.LGCY_IND FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN d, NMST_NOTE_MSTR n WHERE d.NOTE_ID = n.NOTE_ID AND d.ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char((select a.PROD_SYS_ID from CNTRCT_DT_SGMNT a where a.DT_SGMNT_SYS_ID = {0})) AND d.ENTY_TYPE = 'ATTACHPRODUCT' AND N.NOTE_ID NOT IN (SELECT Z.NOTE_ID FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN Z WHERE Z.ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({0}) AND Z.ENTY_TYPE = 'ATTACHCONTRACT') AND n.NOTE_NM LIKE UPPER({1})
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT n.NOTE_ID, n.NOTE_NM, MAX(n.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) NOTE_VRSN_NBR,n.LGCY_IND FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR n , (SELECT DISTINCT A.NOTE_ID from NOTE_DOMN_ASSN A, (SELECT n.NOTE_ID, MAX(n.NOTE_VRSN_NBR) NOTE_VRSN_NBR FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR n WHERE n.NOTE_STTS_CD='PUBLISHED'group by n.NOTE_ID ,n.NOTE_NM ) MSTR WHERE A.NOTE_ID = MSTR.NOTE_ID AND A.NOTE_VRSN_NBR = MSTR.NOTE_VRSN_NBR AND SUBSTR(A.ENTY_TYPE,1,5) = 'AVAIL') b
WHERE n.NOTE_STTS_CD='PUBLISHED' AND n.NOTE_ID = b.NOTE_ID(+) AND b.NOTE_ID is null AND n.NOTE_NM LIKE UPPER({1}) AND n.LGCY_IND = 'N' group by n.NOTE_ID ,n.NOTE_NM,n.LGCY_IND
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT n.NOTE_ID ,n.NOTE_NM , D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR ,n.LGCY_IND FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN d, NMST_NOTE_MSTR n WHERE d.NOTE_ID = n.NOTE_ID AND d.ENTY_TYPE ='LEGACYCONTRACT' AND d.ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({0})
MINUS
SELECT DISTINCT n.NOTE_ID ,n.NOTE_NM , D.NOTE_VRSN_NBR ,n.LGCY_IND FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN d, NMST_NOTE_MSTR n WHERE d.NOTE_ID = n.NOTE_ID AND d.ENTY_TYPE ='ATTACHCONTRACT' AND d.ENTY_SYS_ID = to_char({0})

SQLTemplate.SQLQuery: INSERT INTO NMST_NOTE_MSTR ( NOTE_ID, NOTE_NM, NOTE_TXT, NOTE_TYPE, NOTE_STTS_CD, NOTE_VRSN_NBR, NOTE_PARNT_ID, LST_CHG_USR, LST_CHG_TMS, CREATD_USER_ID, CREATD_TM_STMP, LGCY_IND) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
UPDATE NMST_NOTE_MSTR SET NOTE_NM = ?, NOTE_TXT = ?, NOTE_TYPE = ?, NOTE_STTS_CD = ?, LST_CHG_USR = ?, LST_CHG_TMS = ? WHERE NOTE_ID = ? and NOTE_VRSN_NBR = ?
DELETE FROM NMST_NOTE_MSTR WHERE NOTE_ID = ? and NOTE_VRSN_NBR = ?
INSERT INTO NOTE_DOMN_ASSN (NOTE_ID, ENTY_SYS_ID, ENTY_TYPE, LST_CHG_USR, LST_CHG_TMS, CREATD_USER_ID, CREATD_TM_STMP, NOTE_VRSN_NBR) VALUES(?, ?, 'SYSTEM DOMAIN', ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
DELETE FROM NOTE_DOMN_ASSN WHERE NOTE_ID = ? and NOTE_VRSN_NBR = ?
